#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.46:0.2"
msgid "5. Cakkavattivagga "
msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 46. Daliddasutta → daḷiddasuttaṃ (bj) | daliddo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.46:0.3"
msgid "46. Daliddasutta "
msgstr "46. Poor "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: Daliddo, daliddo’ti → daḷiddo daḷiddoti (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "sn46.46:1.1"
msgid "“‘Daliddo, daliddo’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of someone who is ‘poor’. "

msgctxt "sn46.46:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, ‘daliddo’ti vuccatī”ti? "
msgstr "How is a poor person defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.46:1.3"
msgid "“Sattannaṃ kho, bhikkhu, bojjhaṅgānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā ‘daliddo’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, they’re called poor because they haven’t developed and cultivated the seven awakening factors. "

msgctxt "sn46.46:1.4"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.46:1.5"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgassa … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa—"
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.46:1.6"
msgid "imesaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā ‘daliddo’ti vuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "They’re called poor because they haven’t developed and cultivated these seven awakening factors.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.46:1.7"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

